"ldap" is a LDAP authentication plugin for BIGACE 2.4+.

Instructions to Install:
=========================
1. Sign in as Administrator and install the Extensions

2. Edit the file /system/config/ldap.php and configure you LDAP settings
   using the documentation from the config file. 

3. Edit the file /system/config/services.ini and set the key:
   authenticator = classes.authentication.LDAPAuthenticator 

4. Check website for more infos:
   http://wiki.bigace.de/bigace:extensions:auth:ldap

Post any issue at the Community Forum:
http://forum.bigace.de/
 
Cheers,
Kevin Papst
